ActInternational Development Research Centre Act
PrecisAppointment of ANGELA CROPPER of Port of Spain, the Republic of Trinidad and Tobago, to be governor of the Board of Governors of the International Development Research Centre, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Sir Alister McIntyre, who has resigned.
